data.description:
Welcome to your new haven in Fort Myers, where every day feels like a retreat in this 3-
bedroom plus den, 3-bathroom gem. Everything in this home is brand new, offering you the epitome of modern comfort and convenience. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining friends. Step out onto the spacious screened lanai and bask in the breathtaking views of the surrounding lush landscaping. It's the perfect spot to sip your morning coffee or unwind with a glass of wine in the evening. Beyond the walls of your new home, the Timber Creek Community offers resort-style living with a variety of amenities. Take a dip in the large resort-style pool, savor a meal at the pool cafe & bar, or enjoy a friendly game of pickleball with neighbors. When you're ready to explore the town, you'll be delighted to know that this home's location is central to all of Fort Myers. Make your everyday life extraordinary by calling this gorgeous property your own. Don't wait; this piece of paradise is calling your name!
